data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedrooms, PLUS 3rd Floor Bonus Room! This home features an office/dedicated school room or gym, Open Concept Living room, kitchen & dining all on the first floor. The second floor boasts a huge Master Bedroom with a master bath large enough for a soaking tub, walk-in shower and dual vanities. There are 3 more bedrooms and a beautifully decorated laundry room on the second floor as well. The third floor is massive and has the potential for many uses, including a possible theater. This room is prewired for surround sound. All of this on a large, culdesac lot with extensive decking for entertaining, like new above ground pool, muscadine grape vines all over the backyard, blueberry bushes and elderberry bushes, a chicken coop and fully fenced backyard. You will also find a detached, wired workshop with heating and air, attic space & even has gutters attached.
